43 Cittasaṃsaṭṭhasamuṭṭhānasahabhūduka
Cittasaṃsaṭṭhasamuṭṭhānasahabhūduka
62.
192Nacittasaṃsaṭṭhasamuṭṭhānasahabhuṃ dhammaṃ paṭicca nacittasaṃsaṭṭhasamuṭṭhānasahabhū dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā… . (Saṃkhittaṃ.)
193Hetuyā nava…pe…  avigate nava.
